query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `report_delivery_logs` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `scheduled_report_id` int NOT NULL,
  `report_period_start` timestamp,
  `report_period_end` timestamp,
  `recipients` json,
  `delivery_status` enum('pending','sent','failed') DEFAULT 'pending' NOT NULL,
  `report_file_url` varchar(500),
  `error_message` text,
  `sent_at` timestamp,
  `created_at` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  FOREIGN KEY (`scheduled_report_id`) REFERENCES `scheduled_reports`(`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE,
  INDEX `scheduledReportId_idx` (`scheduled_report_id`),
  INDEX `deliveryStatus_idx` (`delivery_status`),
  INDEX `createdAt_idx` (`created_at`)
)
